import React from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter,Routes,Route} from 'react-router-dom'
import Adminpanel from './adminP/Adminpanel.jsx'
import Navar from './adminP/Navbar.jsx'
const App = () => {
  return (
      <BrowserRouter>
      <Routes>
        <Route exact path='/' element={<Navar></Navar>}>
         <Route path='/adminpanel' element={<Adminpanel></Adminpanel>}></Route>
        </Route>
      </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default App
